The paper presents a method for instance segmentation and object detection, which are both subfields of computer vision (cs.CV). The method also deals with class imbalance and federated annotations, which are common challenges in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the method uses deep learning techniques, which are often discussed in the multimedia (cs.MM) and natural language processing (cs.CL) subfields.
